fm: string toGoatLatin(string S) {         istringstream iss(S);         string ans, buf, a;         while (iss >> buf) {             if (vowels.find(buf[0]) != vowels.end()) {                 ans += buf;             } else {                 ans += buf.substr(1);                 ans += buf[0];             }             ans += "ma";             ans += a += "a";             ans += " ";         }         ans.pop_back();         return ans;     }

fm: vector<vector<int>> flipAndInvertImage(vector<vector<int>>& A) {         for (vector<int> &row : A) {             for (int i = 0; i < (row.size() + 1) / 2; i++) {                 if (row[i] == row[row.size() - i - 1]) {                     row[i] = 1 - row[i];                     row[row.size() - i - 1] = row[i];                 }             }         }         return A;     }

fm: int largestOverlap(vector<vector<int>>& A, vector<vector<int>>& B) {         int max_overlap = 0, n = A.size();         vector<vector<int>> slide(2 * n - 1, vector<int>(2 * n - 1));         for (int ai = 0; ai < n; ai++) {             for (int aj = 0; aj < n; aj++) {                 if (A[ai][aj]) {                     for (int bi = 0; bi < n; bi++) {                         for (int bj = 0; bj < n; bj++) {                             if (B[bi][bj]) {                                 max_overlap = max(max_overlap, ++slide[ai - bi + n - 1][aj - bj + n - 1]);                             }                         }                     }                 }             }         }         return max_overlap;     }

fc: class Solution { public:     bool backspaceCompare(string S, string T) {         return parStr(S) == parStr(T);     }  private:     string parStr(string s) {         int len = 0;         for (char ch : s) {             if (ch == '#' && len > 0) {                 len--;             } else if (islower(ch)) {                 s[len++] = ch;             }         }         return s.substr(0, len);     } };

fm: int peakIndexInMountainArray(vector<int>& A) {         int lo = 1, hi = A.size() - 2;         while (lo <= hi) {             int mid = (lo + hi) / 2;             if (A[mid] < A[mid + 1]) {                 lo = mid + 1;             } else if (A[mid] < A[mid - 1]) {                 hi = mid - 1;             } else {                 return mid;             }         }         throw logic_error("Unreachable code path");     }

fm: int scoreOfParentheses(string S) {         int ans = 0, open = 0;         for (int i = 0; i < S.size(); i++) {             if (S[i] == '(') {                 open++;             } else {                 open--;                 if (S[i - 1] == '(') {                     ans += 1 << open;                 }             }         }         return ans;     }

fm: bool lemonadeChange(vector<int>& bills) {         int c5 = 0, c10 = 0;         for (int b : bills) {             switch (b) {             case 5:                 c5++;                 break;             case 10:                 if (c5 > 0) {                     c5--;                     c10++;                 } else {                     return false;                 }                 break;             case 20:                 if (c5 > 0 && c10 > 0) {                     c5--;                     c10--;                 } else if (c5 > 2) {                     c5 -= 3;                 } else {                     return false;                 }             }         }         return true;     }
